{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"19723-foxy-joxy-plays-a-trick","title":"Foxy Joxy Plays a Trick","description":"Foxy Joxy, a sly fox, sells watermelons. One day he has a clever idea. The animals were not happy. What will they do to teach him a lesson?","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Nahida  Esmail"],"illustrators":["Mdu Ntuli"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Book Dash","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/19723-foxy-joxy-plays-a-trick"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/735188/size3/b90d94b9c65b24e49ac0bf3f5faa5908.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/735188/size6/b90d94b9c65b24e49ac0bf3f5faa5908.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85252/size6/c3bf79e916a12dffd58b5b435da41119.jpg","text":"Foxy Joxy was a sly fox. He sold big, fresh watermelons.\nWatermelons for sale!","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85253/size6/64404f35996255884beadb9c1dc15ef5.jpg","text":"“Your price is too high,” said Rabbit Jabbit.\n“You are asking too much,” said Gia Giraffe.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85254/size6/099af2765c675b14b4f1a2a973408ab8.jpg","text":"Foxy Joxy had a clever idea.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85255/size6/eddf1acd92bb6e301a5619521e940cf9.jpg","text":"He slit open a big watermelon,","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85256/size6/5c962f0fff3d4a17675d1dfd75ba6b71.jpg","text":"scooped out the fruit,","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85257/size6/a4389bad03c1c6ffbac43daa48d9e6ad.jpg","text":"and gobbled it up.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85258/size6/ce2483b61dc0e8f5127d44741550aa3d.jpg","text":"Then he filled it with water!\nHe took a needle and thread and sewed the watermelon back together.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85259/size6/544b4f889d33d11ab879920d1eba5b26.jpg","text":"He sold his watermelons for a cheap price.\nMany animals bought from Foxy Joxy.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85260/size6/5987389388c783aa75c06b80ea39dc7f.jpg","text":"“This watermelon has only water in it,” complained Funky Monkey.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85261/size6/6e8590155ed39e2710f3b5a7c2c67c40.jpg","text":"“Well, you got what you paid for,” said Foxy Joxy.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85262/size6/7e221a084a4031199710d01ffba1e0a8.jpg","text":"“We need to teach Foxy Joxy a lesson,” said Ellie Elephant.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85263/size6/8d8531c62fdefaa02348d59df0c584ce.jpg","text":"The animals gathered around and came up with a plan.\n“I have an idea,” said Oliver Owl.","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85264/size6/32c7b425f68c13f33e38301060ea39d1.jpg","text":"They took an empty \nwatermelon,","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85265/size6/efd3ee2940e3e0f5a31150bee51ecf94.jpg","text":"stuffed Foxy Joxy into it...","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85266/size6/99064f5976dfcd4c0f6cb9763b5e5677.jpg","text":"and played a game of football with it.","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85267/size6/5350b5cac382d9828863793b11cce9da.jpg","text":"Foxy Joxy was dizzy!\nHe learnt his lesson and never cheated again.","words":null},{"n":17,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85268/size6/fc82243214b511ea31a3703baa2bc56e.jpg","text":"18/19","words":null},{"n":18,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/85269/size6/f37ae6b9da448e218f2cf6e7d0ffb044.jpg","text":"19/19","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":18,"words":162}}